QuestData.Title: Barrels, Man
QuestData.Description: I can't believe that giant hozen! He's just throwing barrels everywhere!$b$bBarrels, man!$b$bIt looks like he managed to get pretty much all the pandaren that were working out in front of the brewery. If I were you, I'd help some of them break out. Put some of those ridiculous muscles to use.$b$bWe're headed over to the brewery's rear entrance, to the east. Meet you there!
QuestData.RewardText: What is it with monkeys and barrels, anyway?
